# {{ project_name }}

A Godot {{ godot_version }} C# project.

## Prerequisites

- [.NET runtime](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download) (for GodotEnv and C# build)
- [Python 3](https://www.python.org/downloads/) + [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/)

## Setup

After cloning, run the setup target to install tooling, configure git hooks, and download Godot:

```sh
make setup
```

This installs C# tooling (CSharpier, pre-commit, commitizen) via uv and dotnet, then uses
[GodotEnv](https://github.com/chickensoft-collective/GodotEnv) to download and activate
the correct Godot version (pinned in `.godotrc`).

